title: Ike & Tina Turner - Original Gold (1998)FLAC
description:
Ike & Tina Turner - Original Gold (1998)FLAC

Artist: Ike & Tina Turner
Title: Original Gold
Year Of Release: 1998
Label: Disky [HR 853052]
Genre: Funk, Soul, Rock, Rhythm & Blues
Quality: FLAC
Total Time: 1:44:16


A two-disc set of late-period (1969-1976) Ike and Tina taken largely from the duo's Liberty Records catalog. Although the collection contains a lot of good blues and interesting covers, the EMI Legendary Masters Series single disc has all the earlier Sue Records hits, along with the later hits included here, and is better mastered and more sensibly ordered. For a two-disc set, there's an awful lot of stuff missing from this.
